OL,3,CEmergency alert to hit mobile phones
OL,4,Cin national test - here's what to
OL,5,Cexpect
OL,7,FA loud siren will sound from millions
OL,8,Fof mobile phones this September as the
OL,9,Fgovernment tests its emergency alert
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,FThe emergency alert text will be sent
OL,13,Fto mobile phones across the UK at
OL,14,Faround 3pm on Sunday, September 7, in
OL,15,Fits second-ever nationwide drill.
OL,17,FPhones will vibrate for roughly ten
OL,18,Fseconds - even if they are set to
OL,19,Fsilent - and a message will appear on
OL,20,Fphone screens, making it clear it is a
OL,21,Ftest.
