OL,7,FThe first time the system was tested
OL,8,Fwas in April 2023, but some mobile
OL,9,Fphone users warned that their devices
OL,10,Fdid not sound, with the problem traced
OL,11,Fto specific networks.
OL,13,FWhy is it taking place?
OL,15,FThe emergency alert system is used to
OL,16,Fspread information and advice rapidly,
OL,17,Fand is used to warn if there is a
OL,18,Fdanger to life nearby, in instances
OL,19,Flike extreme weather.
