OL,7,FRegular testing ensures the system is
OL,8,Ffunctioning correctly, should it be
OL,9,Fneeded in an emergency, and
OL,10,Ffamiliarises the public with the
OL,11,Falerts.
OL,13,FWho will and won't receive the alert?
