OL,3,CEmergency alert to hit mobile phones
OL,4,Cin national test - here's what to
OL,5,Cexpect
OL,7,FDuring the test, the UK's
OL,8,Fapproximately 87 million mobile
OL,9,Fdevices will ring out with a high
OL,10,Fpitched alarm and vibrate for
OL,11,Fapproximately 10 seconds, while a
OL,12,Fmessage will appear on the screen
OL,13,Fmaking it clear the alert is only a
OL,14,Ftest.
OL,16,FThe system has already been used in
OL,17,Fseveral scenarios ` including storms,
OL,18,Fflooding and in one case when an
OL,19,Funexploded Second World War bomb was
OL,20,Fdiscovered.
