OL,7,FEmergency alerts work on all 4G and 5G
OL,8,Fphone networks in the UK, and a mobile
OL,9,Fphone or tablet does not have to be
OL,10,Fconnected to mobile data or wifi to
OL,11,Freceive them.
OL,13,FAlerts will not be received if a
OL,14,Fdevice is turned off, connected to a
OL,15,F2G or 3G network, wifi only, or not
OL,16,Fcompatible.
OL,18,FAhead of the national test, ministers
OL,19,Fare spearheading a public awareness
OL,20,Fcampaign to ensure people understand
OL,21,Fwhen it is taking place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
