OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FDomestic violence charities and
OL,13,Fcampaigners are working with victims
OL,14,Fof abuse to ensure they know how to
OL,15,Fswitch off alerts on a concealed phone.
OL,17,FPeople who find themselves in this
OL,18,Fsituation are being told to consult
OL,19,Fdetails about opting out from alerts
OL,20,Fon gov.uk, the Government website.
