OL,7,FDisability charities and campaigners
OL,8,Fare also being consulted to support
OL,9,Fdisabled people, and drivers are being
OL,10,Fencouraged to find somewhere safe and
OL,11,Flegal to stop before reading the
OL,12,Fmessage.
OL,14,FNo personal data will be collected or
OL,15,Fshared as part of the test.
OL,17,FWhen has it been used before?
OL,19,FSince the first national test of the
OL,20,Femergency alerts system in 2023, five
OL,21,Falerts have been sent.
