OL,7,FWhat else is the government doing?
OL,9,FThe government is publishing a
OL,10,FResilience Action Plan on Tuesday to
OL,11,Fimprove the way it prepares for and
OL,12,Fresponds to emergencies, and will
OL,13,Fpublish an update on action being
OL,14,Ftaken to secure the country from
OL,15,Fbiological risks.
OL,17,FPat McFadden, Chancellor of the Duchy
OL,18,Fof Lancaster, is the Cabinet Office
OL,19,Fminister who has taken charge of
OL,20,Fefforts to boost national resilience
OL,21,Fagainst crises.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
