OL,7,FHe said: "Emergency alerts have the
OL,8,Fpotential to save lives, allowing us
OL,9,Fto share essential information rapidly
OL,10,Fin emergency situations including
OL,11,Fextreme storms.
OL,13,F"Just like the fire alarm in your
OL,14,Fhouse, it's important we test the
OL,15,Fsystem so that we know it will work if
OL,16,Fwe need it."
OL,18,FOther countries, including Japan and
OL,19,Fthe USA, also regularly test their
OL,20,Femergency alert systems.
